#### User journey

1. The software prompts the customer when they need to submit an update. This prompt will not be sent from any API.
2. The customer receives the prompt in the software and begins their submission process.
3. Software prepares the summary information and displays it to the customer.
4. The customer checks the information and submits it.
5. The software initiates the data submission process by calling one of the following endpoints, depending on the income source type being submitted:
   - [Create and Amend a Self-Employment Cumulative Period Summary](https://developer.service.hmrc.gov.uk/api-documentation/docs/api/service/self-employment-business-api/5.0/oas/page#tag/Self-Employment-Cumulative-Period-Summary/paths/~1individuals~1business~1self-employment~1%7Bnino%7D~1%7BbusinessId%7D~1cumulative~1%7BtaxYear%7D/put)
   - [Create and Amend a UK Property Cumulative Period Summary](https://developer.service.hmrc.gov.uk/api-documentation/docs/api/service/property-business-api/6.0/oas/page#tag/UK-Property-Cumulative-Period-Summary/paths/~1individuals~1business~1property~1uk~1%7Bnino%7D~1%7BbusinessId%7D~1cumulative~1%7BtaxYear%7D/put)
   - [Create and Amend a Foreign Property Cumulative Period Summary](https://developer.service.hmrc.gov.uk/api-documentation/docs/api/service/property-business-api/6.0/oas/page#tag/Foreign-Property-Cumulative-Period-Summary/paths/~1individuals~1business~1property~1foreign~1%7Bnino%7D~1%7BbusinessId%7D~1cumulative~1%7BtaxYear%7D/put)
6. HMRC receives and stores information and provides a success response.
7. The software receives the success response and confirms with the customer that the update has been received and stored by HMRC.
8. The customer views the confirmation.

#### View update

When a quarterly update has been made, the customer can view a summary of the updates made to date. To retrieve this summary, the software should call any of the following endpoints, depending on the business income type:

- [Retrieve a Self-Employment Cumulative Period Summary](https://developer.service.hmrc.gov.uk/api-documentation/docs/api/service/self-employment-business-api/5.0/oas/page#tag/Self-Employment-Cumulative-Period-Summary/paths/~1individuals~1business~1self-employment~1%7Bnino%7D~1%7BbusinessId%7D~1cumulative~1%7BtaxYear%7D/get)
- [Retrieve a UK Property Cumulative Period Summary](https://developer.service.hmrc.gov.uk/api-documentation/docs/api/service/property-business-api/6.0/oas/page#tag/UK-Property-Cumulative-Period-Summary/paths/~1individuals~1business~1property~1uk~1%7Bnino%7D~1%7BbusinessId%7D~1cumulative~1%7BtaxYear%7D/get)
